fit-landmark 0.1.22 — Landmark — analysis and recommendations on top of Map data.

Usage: fit-landmark <command> [options]

Commands:
  org show          Show full organization directory
  org team          Show hierarchy under a manager
  snapshot list     List available snapshots
  snapshot show     Show factor/driver scores for a snapshot
  snapshot trend    Track item trend across snapshots
  snapshot compare  Compare snapshot against benchmarks
  evidence          Show marker-linked evidence
  practice          Show practice-pattern aggregates
  marker <skill>    Show marker definitions for a skill
  health            Show health view with driver scores and evidence
  readiness         Show promotion readiness checklist
  timeline          Show individual growth timeline
  coverage          Show evidence coverage metrics
  practiced         Show evidenced vs derived capability
  voice             Surface engineer voice from GetDX comments
  sources           List activity row classes retained about an engineer
  login             Sign in via Supabase magic-link (browser or --otp)
  logout            Delete the local credentials file

Options:
  --data=<string>    Path to Map data directory
  --format=<string>  Output format (text|json|markdown)
  --help, -h         Show help
  --version, -v      Show version

Examples:
  fit-landmark org show
  fit-landmark snapshot list
  fit-landmark marker task_completion
  fit-landmark health --manager alice@example.com
  fit-landmark sources --email self@example.com

